{"ja426:0.1":"Jataka ","ja426:0.2":"Atthakanipata ","ja426:0.3":"Kaccanivagga ","ja426:0.4":"10. Dipijataka ","ja426:1.1":"“Khamaniyam yapaniyam, ","ja426:1.2":"kacci matula te sukham; ","ja426:1.3":"Sukham te amma avaca, ","ja426:1.4":"sukhakamava te mayam”. ","ja426:2.1":"“Nanguttham me avakkamma, ","ja426:2.2":"Hethayitvana elike; ","ja426:2.3":"Sajja matulavadena, ","ja426:2.4":"Muncitabba nu mannasi”. ","ja426:3.1":"“Puratthamukho nisinnosi, ","ja426:3.2":"Aham te mukhamagata; ","ja426:3.3":"Pacchato tuyham nanguttham, ","ja426:3.4":"Katham khvaham avakkamim”. ","ja426:4.1":"“Yavata caturo dipa, ","ja426:4.2":"sasamudda sapabbata; ","ja426:4.3":"Tavata mayham nanguttham, ","ja426:4.4":"katham kho tvam vivajjayi”. ","ja426:5.1":"“Pubbeva metamakkhimsu, ","ja426:5.2":"mata pita ca bhataro; ","ja426:5.3":"Digham dutthassa nanguttham, ","ja426:5.4":"samhi vehayasagata”. ","ja426:6.1":"“Tanca disvana ayantim, ","ja426:6.2":"antalikkhasmi elike; ","ja426:6.3":"Migasangho palayittha, ","ja426:6.4":"bhakkho me nasito taya”. ","ja426:7.1":"“Iccevam vilapantiya, ","ja426:7.2":"elakiya ruhagghaso; ","ja426:7.3":"Galakam anvavamaddi, ","ja426:7.4":"natthi dutthe subhasitam. ","ja426:8.1":"Neva dutthe nayo atthi, ","ja426:8.2":"Na dhammo na subhasitam; ","ja426:8.3":"Nikkamam dutthe yunjetha, ","ja426:8.4":"So ca sabbhim na ranjati”ti. ","ja426:9.1":"Dipijatakam dasamam. ","ja426:10.1":"Atthakanipatam nitthitam. ","ja426:11.1":"Tassuddanam ","ja426:12.1":"Parisuddha manavila vatthadhara, ","ja426:12.2":"Bakarajassa kayuram dandavaro; ","ja426:12.3":"Atha angara cetiya devilina, ","ja426:12.4":"Atha aditta ganga daselakinati. "}